org.batfish.grammar

Class BatfishParserATNSimulator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.antlr.v4.runtime.atn.ATNSimulator
      • org.antlr.v4.runtime.atn.ParserATNSimulator
        • org.batfish.grammar.BatfishParserATNSimulator

  • public class BatfishParserATNSimulator
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.atn.ParserATNSimulator
    Clones an existing ParserATNSimulator used by a BatfishParser and wraps the adaptivePredict(org.antlr.v4.runtime.TokenStream, int, org.antlr.v4.runtime.ParserRuleContext) function with a recovery mechanism. Intended for use with a BatfishParser employing a BatfishANTLRErrorStrategy as its error recovery strategy.
